Package com.igormaznitsa.prol.data

The package contains classes describe data types used by the engine.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
ConvertableToTerm The interface must be implemented by a Java object which can be represented as a Prolog term
NumericTerm The interface describes a numeric term and its possible operations
 

Class Summary
Operator This class represents a prolog operator
Term It is the main core class for all objects in the engine which represent terms.
TermFloat The class describes a ground term which can save a float value
TermInteger The class describes a ground term which can save an integer value
TermList The term represents a prolog list
TermStruct The class describing the prolog structure
Var The class contains the prolog var implementation, very important class for engine work.
